// Invoke Bedrock Model for Resource Exhaustion (T1496) — eventName(s) auto-derived; verify casing.
// Signal: bedrock:InvokeModel called at high volume or from an unexpected principal; sudden spike in Bedrock spend in cost explorer
AWSCloudTrail
| where EventName in ("InvokeModel")
| project TimeGenerated, UserIdentityArn, EventName, SourceIpAddress, AWSRegion
| order by TimeGenerated desc
